Revision history for Data-Format-Pretty-YAML

0.07    2014-02-14 (SHARYANTO)

	- Change default of linum from 1 when pretty/interactive to 0 to avoid
          potential annoyance for users trying to copy paste output.


0.06    2013-11-12 (SHARYANTO)

	- No functional changes. Rebuild to fix t/00-compile.t generated by
	  older DZP::Test::Compile (2.019 < x < 2.033).


0.05     2013-09-29 (SHARYANTO)

         - Add settings: linum & pretty.


0.04     2012-11-18 (SHARYANTO)

         - Observe environment COLOR.


0.03     2012-11-16 (SHARYANTO)

         - Yay, now use YAML::Tiny::Color when interactive.


0.02     2012-03-29 (SHARYANTO)

         - Add content_type().


0.01     2011-08-11 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release.
